data.description: Lovely Tri-Level 4 bedroom, 2 bath with tons of space inside and out. Located at the end of a culd-de-sec with mature trees.  Large fenced in backyard which is great for entertaining on wonderful summer days. Mini barns with lots of storage for workspace or crafting activites.   This wonderful home has hardwood floors and some covered by carpet, a gas fireplace and large family room, great for movies and playspace for the kids.  Finished 2 car garage, paved driveway with a second area of storage as well.  Don't miss this opprtunity so schedule your showing today!!
